    "severity": "medium",
    "description": "The getCommentLikes method fetches the comment but doesn't verify it exists. This is inconsistent with other methods like getCommentByID which use {require: true}. Without this check, the endpoint won't distinguish between a comment with no likes and a non-existent comment, and will return an empty result instead of throwing an error.",
