    "file": "ghost/core/core/server/services/comments/comments-service.js",
    "line": 266,
    "severity": "high",
    "description": "The withRelated array is empty, but the feature is to display members who have liked comments. Without including the 'member' relation, the API will return only IDs without member details, breaking the intended functionality. The parallel method getCommentReporters correctly uses withRelated: ['member'].",
